584: 		// Reorder plugins. Here is the expected order:
585: 		// - part 1: overridePlugins. Their order stay intact as how they're specified in regular extension point.
586: 		// - part 2: multiPointEnabled - i.e., plugin defined in multipoint but not in regular extension point.
